    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>VOIDFACE</strong>, you face off in a challenging bullet-hell arena shooter to try and clear bite-sized boss rush challenges. Learn to dodge their attacks, cast spells to gain an upper hand, and kill everything that gets in your way.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224540/extras/dd06f6fcd16d22909bd7c0e3905d7533.poster.avif?t=1770854211\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224540/extras/dd06f6fcd16d22909bd7c0e3905d7533.webm?t=1770854211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224540/extras/dd06f6fcd16d22909bd7c0e3905d7533.mp4?t=1770854211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >27 unique bosses, across 9 stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial and finale stage, with special bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy and hard mode (easy mode is still quite challenging!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One hit, and you're dead (2 HP on easy mode)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various defensive and offensive spells </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized, smooth-rendered pixel graphics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A banger soundtrack with dynamic layering for each stage  </p></li></ul>",
